creator: Loyal Softwares
descriptionHtml:
Tp link modem is one of the most used router brands in the world. Our mobile app describes how to set up and configure the tp link modem.

Application content;

* How to access the modem interface? (Usually 192.168.l.l ip address is used to make "tp link login", but depending on the modem model, sometimes it can be accessed via the internet address provided on the back of the device.)

* How to manage user? (Describes how to add and delete users to the modem.)

* How to change the tp link admin password (the default router login information is used at the first login. Then you will have to change it with a hard-to-guess password for your device security)

* How to change the TP LINK wifi password (the wireless password should be changed every 3 months, such as preventing hacking. In this way, you can prevent your neighbors and friends from using your internet once and for all).

* 192.168.l.l tp link modem password change and ip address change

* and how to: bridge mode setting, tp link wifi settings, remote control and modem reset
descriptionShort: This app will help you to configure easily you tp link settings.
